&lt;p&gt;Support is Help Scout&#39;s bread and butter. We’re pleased to be searching for our sixth, full-time support team member. Our ideal hire is motivated by what we&#39;re doing as a company, and eager to contribute on the front lines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
